OL,3,GHighlands & Eilean Siar
OL,4,
OL,5,CToday:FAll parts will have a dry day.
OL,6,FCloud will lift and break through the
OL,7,Fmorning to give some sunshine this
OL,8,Fafternoon, although cloud may linger
OL,9,Falong Moray Firth coastal areas.
OL,10,
OL,11,CTonight:FDry this evening with some
OL,12,Flate sunshine in most places. Then
OL,13,Fstaying dry overnight but cloud will
OL,14,Fspread inland from the east. Skye and
OL,15,FLochaber staying mostly clear. Patchy
OL,16,Ffrost.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
OL,24,ANext Page  BWeather  CReg News  FReg TV
