OL,3,GHighlands & Eilean Siar
OL,4,
OL,5,CWednesday:FA dry day. Overnight cloud
OL,6,Fwill gradually lift and break to allow
OL,7,Fsome sunny intervals by afternoon.
OL,8,FBest of the sunshine across Skye and
OL,9,FLochaber. Warm in the southwest.
OL,10,
OL,11,COutlook for Thursday to Saturday:
OL,12,FStaying dry with plenty of sunshine
OL,13,Fonce any overnight cloud has cleared.
OL,14,FWarm in the sunshine. Light winds.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
